main event: A UFO sighting was reported in Des Moines, Iowa on 29 June 1947.
interesting points: The sighting was recorded at 1645 CST.,The object was described as an inverted saucer.,The estimated diameter of the object was between 175 to 225 feet.,The speed of the object was reported to be 300 mph.,A total of 13 objects were sighted in the group.
